asd san giorgio a cremano (also known as 'san giorgio calcio', and 'san giorgio 1926') is an italian association football club, first founded in 1926, and based in san giorgio a cremano, campania. the club currently competes in the eccellenza campania – group a, having been relegated from group a in the 2011–12 season. they play their home games at "stadio comunale raffaele paudice", on via sandriana, in san giorgio a cremano, and wear an all-maroon kit.